{"tid":1961828,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"從615到今天的血債 - 陳也","createTime":"2020-04-07T05:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:56:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"f60f5e11ea4d92cd2d791cf6c7e0f0836590f931","tid":1961828,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-07T05:10:24.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200407/20895068/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200407%2F20895068%2F&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le3dC2y4sA4GELDQI6FTBpyI%3D&h=5e37c726\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%2599%25B3%25E4%25B9%259F%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200407%2F20895068%2F&h=4a63c014\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%99%B3%E4%B9%9F/daily/article/20200407/20895068/</a><br />\n<br />\n從615到今天的血債 - 陳也<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200407/large/1586161592_5300.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200407%2Flarge%2F1586161592_5300.jpg&h=dc7313bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香港電台《鏗鏘集》截圖<br />\n<br />\n特首又再表演哽咽？請高抬貴手，這次，不要貓哭老鼠，露出口罩上的兇狠目光，卻忘記搽紫花油，成功爭取不到擠壓淚腺後，說「你們為了出去食碗車仔麵&hellip;&hellip;對得住班（醫護）同事咩&hellip;&hellip;！」特首你次次做武肺記招主角，攬晒抗疫大權於一身，有無諗過，幫手善後的特首辦新聞主任，等同替你的遺容上妝，明明醜爛變形，都得大修大補，將你執番靚，靚過靚次伯！大嬸變索女，新聞主任這份工，除了超人擔當到，凡人肯定壓力大，機器壞。特首你，對住鏡頭哽咽，回到辦公室咆吼，變臉玩謝下屬，這種老細，就算冇確診武肺都屬假陰性，都要保持社交距離，堅守點五米的空間。可惜，特首辦新聞主任，不是PK鄧的三萬步兵，後者除了虐打精神殘障人士，更可以聚餐BBQ後圍毆長洲市民，大剌剌反問「未見過差佬打人咩」，勁似元朗721白衫社團的對白。黑警心繫佢份工，有後台撐，等住加人工領九億補水開香檳，會企跳？第二世啦！最得老細歡心亦唔驚失業的香港黑警，全球唯一，其他打工族，冇咁好彩。特首辦新聞主任，縱身一跳，換回特首辦晚上回應一句「深感震驚及悲痛」。完。不，血債，未完。 <br />\n<br />\n陳也<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"b66363706fb25b7d7ae43da8ece9fc45ce40b00c","tid":1961828,"uid":187489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T03:34:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ce4c6c02cec19f5b9612cf17ad890309a3b438f","tid":1961828,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6acad539d9710519c9c9e3dd57b159ae55266c84","tid":1961828,"uid":78519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:56:45.000Z","msg":"615黑衫白絲帶<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}